__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
nul
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage test-artifacts (subprocess-coverage from tests/conftest.py)
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/

# Per-run hardening artifacts (captured by scripts/hardening-run.py).
# Markdown reports stay; only the log subdirs are gitignored because they
# leak absolute paths / env-specific data. Reports reference these files
# but the expectation is: reviewers re-run hardening-run.py locally to
# regenerate evidence.
oversight/hardening-*/
!oversight/hardening-*.md

# Per-user self-improving state. Every user of the plugin builds their own
# corrections/memory over time. The committed template lives at
# self-improving/corrections.md.example.
self-improving/corrections.md
self-improving/memory.md
